ore membranes in dead-end filtration, (b) the membranes'\ninteraction with their surroundings due to neighboring membranes, and (c) the\neffect of the used fluid system for displacement on the resulting wetting\npatterns.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Apr 2022 13:53:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-12"}
