ght $\\RC$ eigenvalue $b$.\nThe set $\\RC$ $\\mathrm{spec}(a)$ of all left and right $\\RC$ eigenvalues is\ncalled $\\RC$ spectrum of the matrix a.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Apr 2022 05:13:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-01"}
